Insider Activity


Individual




Henry R. Slack



Mr. Henry R. Slack is Chairman at Alico, Inc. and Senior Partner at Quarterwatch LLC. He is on the Board of Directors at E. Oppenheimer & Son International Ltd. and Raritan Headquarters Association. Mr. Slack was previously employed as Chairman by First Africa Group Holdings Pty Ltd, Chairman by Task (USA), Inc., Chief Executive Officer by Minorco SA, and Chairman by Terra Industries, Inc. He also served on the board at Southern African Breweries Plc, Solomon Brothers, Anglo American Corp. of South Africa Ltd., Engelhard Corp., African Gold Plc and BASF Catalysts LLC. He received his undergraduate degree from Princeton University.



