Henry R. Slack

Age : 66Public asset : 317,319 USDLinked companies :  Alico, Inc. 





Summary 



Mr. Henry R. Slack is Executive Chairman at Alico, Inc. and Senior Partner at Quarterwatch LLC.He is on the Board of Directors at E. Oppenheimer & Son International Ltd., Castleton Commodities International LLC and Raritan Headquarters Association. Mr. Slack was previously employed as Chairman by First Africa Group Holdings Pty Ltd, Chairman by Task (USA), Inc., Chief Executive Officer by Minorco SA, and Chairman by Terra Industries, Inc.He also served on the board at SABMiller Plc, Solomon Brothers, Anglo American Corp. of South Africa Ltd., Engelhard Corp., African Gold Plc and BASF Catalysts LLC.He received his undergraduate degree from Princeton University.



